1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:03.480
US, US

3
00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:09.340
US, ALL OF US

4
00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:15.770
The end of the dream, the end of the sea

5
00:00:15.770 --> 00:00:17.750
We all have different places we want to go WE ALL HAVE DIFFERENT PLACES WE WANT TO GO

6
00:00:15.790 --> 00:00:18.530
We all have different places we want to go

7
00:00:18.530 --> 00:00:21.310
But to start we've got to show what we're made of

8
00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:25.660
We'll be legends, we're gonna take the world by storm

9
00:00:26.930 --> 00:00:29.250
Sparks are flying, NO LIMITS! This is where it starts

10
00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:30.530
ONE PIECE!!

11
00:00:30.890 --> 00:00:33.510
VORONOI START VORONOI END ALL OF US, I've got a question for you

12
00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:37.100
Have you let the world and all its burdens bring your dreams down?

13
00:00:38.740 --> 00:00:45.300
Every cell in me is getting restless - They're about to blow, oh, it's just too much Every cell in me is getting restless - They're about to blow, oh, it's just too much

14
00:00:45.410 --> 00:00:52.030
Still we try, ALL OF US have our own paths we cling to

15
00:00:52.030 --> 00:00:54.620
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you

16
00:00:53.620 --> 00:00:55.150
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall

17
00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:58.200
If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall

18
00:00:59.890 --> 00:01:02.580
Random clues suddenly fit together

19
00:01:02.580 --> 00:01:06.510
Starting to make sense, oh, what's going on?

20
00:01:06.510 --> 00:01:12.980
Threads of time weaving into an intricate tapestry

21
00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:18.680
We can't stop the world from turning, it's changing along with every one of-

22
00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.250
US, US

23
00:01:21.870 --> 00:01:26.360
US, ALL OF US

24
00:01:38.580 --> 00:01:40.660
You almost stepped on us, man!

25
00:01:40.660 --> 00:01:43.370
My bad, my bad!

26
00:01:46.460 --> 00:01:47.800
My...

27
00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:51.590
You've certainly grown...

28
00:01:51.590 --> 00:01:54.300
I'm not letting you take Apple Gramps.

29
00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:57.430
I'd appreciate it if you'd just...

30
00:01:57.930 --> 00:02:01.140
let me do my job, please.

31
00:02:02.350 --> 00:02:04.770
No can do!

32
00:02:17.950 --> 00:02:19.830
Whoa, now...

33
00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:26.000
Here we go!

34
00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:35.550
Go easy on me...

35
00:02:37.890 --> 00:02:39.890
if you wouldn't mind!

36
00:02:50.780 --> 00:02:56.200
<b>Luffy vs. Kizaru</b>

37
00:02:52.030 --> 00:02:54.450
Look at him go!

38
00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:00.160
We gotta run before it's too late!

39
00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:03.620
Yeah, while Luffy is keeping Kizaru busy!

40
00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:06.620
We'll have to be careful carrying Robin!

41
00:03:08.210 --> 00:03:11.050
Where are you going, Atlas?!

42
00:03:11.050 --> 00:03:14.510
I'm going down there to take back
control of the pacifista!

43
00:03:14.510 --> 00:03:16.180
Otherwise...

44
00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:18.220
as soon as the barrier goes down...

45
00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:25.140
they'll blast us with their lasers!

46
00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:26.940
What a capital idea!

47
00:03:26.940 --> 00:03:29.730
Vegapunk's the highest authority
on this here island!

48
00:03:29.730 --> 00:03:32.440
And whoever controls the pacifista wins!

49
00:03:33.940 --> 00:03:36.030
Damn right! I'm off!

50
00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:37.740
Wait, Atlas!

51
00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:40.740
Er, what I mean is...

52
00:03:40.740 --> 00:03:42.990
I... I'll go with you!

53
00:03:42.990 --> 00:03:43.620
– What?!
– What?!

54
00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:46.210
There's no way you're going!

55
00:03:46.210 --> 00:03:47.040
Why not?

56
00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:51.540
This whole thing is happening
because they're trying to kill you!

57
00:03:51.540 --> 00:03:52.630
Yes, but...

58
00:03:53.090 --> 00:03:54.670
Hey, Franky!

59
00:03:54.670 --> 00:03:56.800
Franky, can you hear me?!

60
00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.630
Yeah!

61
00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.800
It seems like Bonney is down there!

62
00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:02.180
She's alive?! That's great news!

63
00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:05.060
Kizaru kicked her hard—right into the barrier!

64
00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:06.810
He kicked her?!

65
00:04:06.810 --> 00:04:10.230
Aren't you a grown man?!
How could you let her get kicked?!

66
00:04:10.230 --> 00:04:11.690
I get it, man! My bad!

67
00:04:12.060 --> 00:04:13.690
I'll go save her right now!

68
00:04:13.690 --> 00:04:14.650
You'd better!

69
00:04:14.650 --> 00:04:16.780
But there's still the barrier...

70
00:04:19.030 --> 00:04:20.530
That's it! I'm going too!

71
00:04:20.530 --> 00:04:21.120
What?

72
00:04:21.620 --> 00:04:23.870
Edison can deactivate the barrier.

73
00:04:27.580 --> 00:04:29.210
Hello?!

74
00:04:29.210 --> 00:04:30.960
<b>Second Floor
Building A</b>

75
00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:32.710
This is Sanji speaking!

76
00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:39.630
If you're gonna rescue Bonney, count me in!

77
00:04:40.010 --> 00:04:44.350
Vegapunk. We've picked up
the luggage you mentioned.

78
00:04:44.850 --> 00:04:47.180
I'll head toward the rear exit!

79
00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:48.980
Let's all meet up there!

80
00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:51.650
Go, go, go!

81
00:04:49.020 --> 00:04:53.190
<b>Below
In the Fabriophase</b>

82
00:04:51.650 --> 00:04:52.560
Oh, crap!

83
00:04:54.110 --> 00:04:55.230
What was that?

84
00:04:55.230 --> 00:04:56.940
Hey, you there!

85
00:04:56.940 --> 00:04:58.690
Get a move on! It's this way!

86
00:04:58.690 --> 00:04:59.570
Yes, sir!

87
00:05:03.780 --> 00:05:05.660
Guess I'm not safe here, either.

88
00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:20.050
Over here!

89
00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:29.310
What was that?!

90
00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:32.270
Come in!

91
00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:33.600
What's going on?!

92
00:05:34.190 --> 00:05:34.940
You little...

93
00:05:35.730 --> 00:05:36.480
Hey, stop!

94
00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:39.780
You're...

95
00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.490
Jewelry–

96
00:05:50.500 --> 00:05:53.330
Town central team! Give me a status report!

97
00:05:53.330 --> 00:05:54.670
W-Well...

98
00:05:54.670 --> 00:05:55.380
Why, you...!

99
00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:18.400
D-Dammit...

100
00:06:20.070 --> 00:06:21.030
Report!

101
00:06:21.610 --> 00:06:24.570
We've all been turned into
children and seniors!

102
00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:26.820
Dammit!

103
00:06:26.820 --> 00:06:29.830
Stay away from the center of town!

104
00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:32.660
We believe the pirate Jewelry Bonney is there!

105
00:06:33.410 --> 00:06:35.630
She must be hiding somewhere! Be on guard!

106
00:06:35.630 --> 00:06:38.000
She'll manipulate your age!

107
00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.920
It's too heavy!

108
00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:41.130
Where'd that blasted kid get off to?

109
00:06:41.130 --> 00:06:42.420
She must be nearby!

110
00:06:42.420 --> 00:06:46.090
Find Bonney and take her out!

111
00:06:48.220 --> 00:06:49.220
Damn...

112
00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:50.680
Hey, over here!

113
00:06:51.810 --> 00:06:53.600
Sentomaru has been located!

114
00:06:54.140 --> 00:06:55.390
But...

115
00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:58.810
he's burned to a crisp.

116
00:06:59.570 --> 00:07:01.110
Sentomaru...

117
00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:15.620
S-Sentomaru!

118
00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:17.500
Bonney...

119
00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:19.090
Run...

120
00:07:19.460 --> 00:07:21.840
The Marines are coming...

121
00:07:27.760 --> 00:07:29.100
Sentomaru!

122
00:07:31.010 --> 00:07:32.220
What should I do?

123
00:07:32.220 --> 00:07:32.970
Was she there?

124
00:07:32.970 --> 00:07:33.770
No, sir!

125
00:07:33.770 --> 00:07:34.680
Go check that way!

126
00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:35.560
Yes, sir!

127
00:07:37.900 --> 00:07:40.940
Can I stay hidden until this all blows over?

128
00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:45.490
<b>Labophase</b>

129
00:07:47.820 --> 00:07:48.950
Hey!

130
00:07:48.950 --> 00:07:50.830
Get out here already!

131
00:07:52.030 --> 00:07:54.910
Let us do our job, Roronoa.

132
00:07:55.290 --> 00:07:58.120
Don't get in our way!

133
00:08:09.010 --> 00:08:11.100
It doesn't matter if you hide...

134
00:08:11.850 --> 00:08:14.020
It doesn't matter if you move around...

135
00:08:14.430 --> 00:08:16.100
I know exactly where you are...

136
00:08:17.980 --> 00:08:20.400
because you stink like an animal!

137
00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:07.070
You're really going at it!

138
00:09:07.070 --> 00:09:10.070
Zoro! Want a hand?

139
00:09:13.070 --> 00:09:15.530
I'm just... fine!

140
00:09:21.290 --> 00:09:24.250
Just focus on Kizaru!

141
00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:47.610
If this is the best you can do,

142
00:09:48.150 --> 00:09:52.570
don't expect to get another shot
at facing our captain.

143
00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:56.080
Whatever you say.

144
00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:58.450
You're still an Emperor's right-hand man.

145
00:09:58.450 --> 00:10:00.540
You're well worth killing on your own.

146
00:10:19.220 --> 00:10:20.770
Seems like...

147
00:10:21.350 --> 00:10:23.350
I'm falling toward the ocean.

148
00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:33.820
Sacred Yasakani Jewel.

149
00:10:54.550 --> 00:10:55.930
What the?!

150
00:10:59.510 --> 00:11:01.430
– Sacred Murakumo Sword.
– Sacred Murakumo Sword.

151
00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:24.580
Ouch! That smarts!

152
00:11:24.580 --> 00:11:26.040
Gum-Gum...

153
00:11:29.170 --> 00:11:30.090
Dawn...

154
00:11:30.790 --> 00:11:33.170
Whip!

155
00:11:39.010 --> 00:11:40.550
It didn't work!

156
00:11:40.550 --> 00:11:41.930
Was it a holo-holo?!

157
00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:47.100
So shiny!

158
00:11:47.100 --> 00:11:48.520
It's so bright!

159
00:11:48.520 --> 00:11:50.810
Whoopsie!

160
00:11:55.530 --> 00:11:57.490
This again?

161
00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:22.810
Well, that's fine. A bigger target
makes my job easier.

162
00:12:22.810 --> 00:12:24.270
Appreciate the help.

163
00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:48.370
Which one's real?!

164
00:12:57.010 --> 00:12:58.220
Just kidding!

165
00:12:58.800 --> 00:12:59.680
Tricked ya!

166
00:13:00.010 --> 00:13:01.890
Gum-Gum...

167
00:13:01.890 --> 00:13:03.850
Dawn...

168
00:13:05.640 --> 00:13:07.730
Stamp!

169
00:13:26.290 --> 00:13:28.370
Did I get the real one too?

170
00:13:36.800 --> 00:13:39.590
I'm the one who got tricked!

171
00:13:39.590 --> 00:13:42.300
Now, that's strange.

172
00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:45.930
Where did Vegapunk go?

173
00:13:45.930 --> 00:13:48.270
Could you tell me?

174
00:13:48.270 --> 00:13:50.980
L-Luffy!

175
00:14:03.860 --> 00:14:06.200
Apple Gramps!

176
00:14:06.620 --> 00:14:10.410
Wait! Let me in, Vegapunk!

177
00:14:11.330 --> 00:14:12.830
What's going on?!

178
00:14:12.830 --> 00:14:14.250
You seem pissed!

179
00:14:14.250 --> 00:14:17.130
You better keep your hands
off her, you lousy Marines!

180
00:14:17.130 --> 00:14:20.760
I'm coming to save you, Bonney!

181
00:14:20.760 --> 00:14:24.390
How could I leave that innocent child to die?!

182
00:14:24.390 --> 00:14:25.970
Innocent child?

183
00:14:25.970 --> 00:14:27.850
Get in already!

184
00:14:27.850 --> 00:14:31.020
I'll let you ride with us!
Just squeeze yourself in wherever!

185
00:14:31.480 --> 00:14:33.190
Squeeze myself in?

186
00:14:41.860 --> 00:14:44.570
What are you doing?! Stay in the lab!

187
00:14:44.570 --> 00:14:46.990
You're gonna get yourself killed!

188
00:14:49.620 --> 00:14:52.000
Where do you think you're going...

189
00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:56.210
Vegapunk?

190
00:14:56.210 --> 00:14:58.710
Crap, crap, crap! We gotta move, Stella!

191
00:15:19.310 --> 00:15:20.730
He's back already?!

192
00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:23.440
Stella?!

193
00:15:23.440 --> 00:15:24.700
Lilith!

194
00:15:24.700 --> 00:15:27.490
Use the General Franky to carry the ship!

195
00:15:28.160 --> 00:15:30.080
I'll catch this ride and meet you there!

196
00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:31.580
You got it!

197
00:15:59.190 --> 00:16:00.900
Edison! Now!

198
00:16:00.900 --> 00:16:02.400
Comin' right up!

199
00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:03.860
Frontier Dome,

200
00:16:03.860 --> 00:16:05.740
partially deactivatin'!

201
00:16:07.910 --> 00:16:09.530
Initiatin' reactivation!

202
00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:14.660
We're falling! We're falling!

203
00:16:25.670 --> 00:16:27.420
H-Hey, look!

204
00:16:28.300 --> 00:16:29.890
Wait a second...

205
00:16:29.890 --> 00:16:31.850
I-I thought so... That's...

206
00:16:32.850 --> 00:16:34.810
Dr. Vegapunk!

207
00:16:35.390 --> 00:16:39.100
<b>Off the Coast of Egghead</b>

208
00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:39.100
This is the Fabriophase team on the island!

209
00:16:39.100 --> 00:16:40.400
I have a report!

210
00:16:40.400 --> 00:16:44.650
Dr. Vegapunk is descending
from the Labophase!

211
00:16:44.650 --> 00:16:47.030
Prepare to attack! Aim!

212
00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:57.870
Attention, all pacifista!

213
00:16:58.460 --> 00:17:02.460
Vegapunk has new orders for you!

214
00:17:02.460 --> 00:17:04.750
Wipe out every Marine...

215
00:17:06.800 --> 00:17:10.800
on this entire island!

216
00:17:38.620 --> 00:17:39.750
Oh no...

217
00:17:39.750 --> 00:17:41.420
It's our turn now...

218
00:17:42.460 --> 00:17:44.330
Objective updated.

219
00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:47.800
Wipe out all Marines.

220
00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:55.470
Get away from the pacifista!

221
00:18:04.100 --> 00:18:08.110
Vegapunk must have overridden their orders!

222
00:18:13.450 --> 00:18:17.120
Shit! I can't believe we lost the pacifista!

223
00:18:18.830 --> 00:18:20.580
Damn you, Vegapunk!

224
00:18:21.540 --> 00:18:24.250
That's the stuff, pacifista!

225
00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:28.630
Keep givin' 'em hell!

226
00:18:29.250 --> 00:18:31.630
Looks like it worked!

227
00:18:31.630 --> 00:18:32.550
Yeah!

228
00:18:35.800 --> 00:18:36.510
Hey!

229
00:18:36.890 --> 00:18:40.020
How are we going straight down?!

230
00:18:40.020 --> 00:18:41.600
Shouldn't we be falling?!

231
00:18:41.600 --> 00:18:45.850
A property of island clouds
is that they stick to each other.

232
00:18:45.850 --> 00:18:51.400
The tires on the Vegatank are made
of island clouds, so it won't fall!

233
00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:54.860
But enough about that. Atlas! Locate Bonney!

234
00:18:54.860 --> 00:18:57.870
She must feel alone and scared!

235
00:18:57.870 --> 00:18:59.490
Bonney!

236
00:18:59.490 --> 00:19:02.370
Where are you?! Bonney!

237
00:19:02.370 --> 00:19:03.790
Bonney!

238
00:19:03.790 --> 00:19:06.290
Bonney...!

239
00:19:13.880 --> 00:19:15.260
I have to focus!

240
00:19:16.130 --> 00:19:17.760
Feel her essence!

241
00:19:19.140 --> 00:19:20.810
I have to give Bonney...

242
00:19:21.100 --> 00:19:23.430
my entire heart and soul!

243
00:19:34.570 --> 00:19:36.490
I got a ping on my lady-dar!

244
00:19:36.490 --> 00:19:37.700
I found her!

245
00:19:38.450 --> 00:19:39.700
Where is she?!

246
00:19:39.700 --> 00:19:41.700
All I see are Marines!

247
00:19:41.700 --> 00:19:44.200
Are you sure, Sanji?!

248
00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:46.960
Has my radar ever been wrong?!

249
00:19:46.960 --> 00:19:48.830
Well, no...

250
00:19:48.830 --> 00:19:53.340
Scientific or not... I'll trust you anyway!

251
00:19:53.340 --> 00:19:54.720
Appreciate that!

252
00:19:55.340 --> 00:19:57.050
Although, this tank...

253
00:19:57.550 --> 00:20:00.510
is too slow to keep up
with my impatient heart!

254
00:20:02.970 --> 00:20:06.520
I'll be right there, Bonney!

255
00:20:08.350 --> 00:20:09.980
What a relief...

256
00:20:10.610 --> 00:20:12.860
The pacifista are on our side again.

257
00:20:23.740 --> 00:20:25.830
I finally found you!

258
00:20:25.830 --> 00:20:28.920
The pirate... Jewelry Bonney!

259
00:20:28.330 --> 00:20:31.290
<b>Vice Admiral Pomsky
Marine Headquarters</b>

260
00:20:28.920 --> 00:20:31.290
How dare you do that to my men!

261
00:20:32.540 --> 00:20:34.300
Found her! She's over here!

262
00:20:42.140 --> 00:20:44.100
Near-Death Experience!

263
00:21:11.750 --> 00:21:14.290
Hey! What happened to you guys?!

264
00:21:14.290 --> 00:21:17.380
I saw the river Styx...

265
00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:21.470
Get back here, Bonney!

266
00:21:25.600 --> 00:21:26.970
You will not escape!

267
00:21:29.600 --> 00:21:30.440
What?!

268
00:21:31.310 --> 00:21:32.690
Why?!

269
00:21:33.650 --> 00:21:38.570
It might be just the one, but I can control it
no matter what the authority hierarchy says!

270
00:21:39.820 --> 00:21:42.700
I command anything I ride!

271
00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:45.530
<b>Vice Admiral Bluegrass
Marine Headquarters</b>

272
00:21:42.700 --> 00:21:45.530
I'm a driver lady who ate the Ride-Ride Fruit!

273
00:21:45.530 --> 00:21:50.750
If I kill you, will it lift the curse
you placed on our men?!

274
00:21:56.670 --> 00:21:58.510
Dad...

275
00:21:58.510 --> 00:22:02.720
Give them back their proper ages!

276
00:22:12.020 --> 00:22:14.230
Bonney, you need to pay attention!

277
00:22:16.310 --> 00:22:17.820
Black Leg!

278
00:22:18.570 --> 00:22:21.530
Y'know, I heard Kuma is your father.

279
00:22:25.530 --> 00:22:28.540
But you have to remember
those aren't him! Or else you...

280
00:22:31.250 --> 00:22:33.750
Otter Hammer!

281
00:22:36.500 --> 00:22:38.300
They just keep coming!

282
00:22:40.880 --> 00:22:42.260
Guess we should run for it!

283
00:22:42.260 --> 00:22:45.760
Don't let them escape, pacifista!

284
00:22:47.470 --> 00:22:48.930
What?!

285
00:22:55.310 --> 00:22:57.360
Bonney!

286
00:23:00.190 --> 00:23:02.530
Sanji, Bonney! Get in!

287
00:23:04.110 --> 00:23:07.620
The pacifista are on our side now!
Let's head back up!

288
00:23:07.620 --> 00:23:09.740
Shake it off already!

289
00:23:10.740 --> 00:23:12.000
Ouch!

290
00:23:44.820 --> 00:23:50.370
<b>Labophase</b>

291
00:24:04.970 --> 00:24:07.090
There's no use resisting!

292
00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:08.800
You don't stand a chance!

293
00:24:09.930 --> 00:24:12.010
This guy never learns.

294
00:24:33.990 --> 00:24:37.290
We have our own reasons
for doing this too, you know.

295
00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:42.460
Don't care!

296
00:24:53.890 --> 00:24:56.730
This is the end of the line for you guys!

297
00:24:59.390 --> 00:25:02.020
You can bark all you want!

298
00:25:12.570 --> 00:25:19.210
Apologies, but if I spend all my time on you,
I won't be able to complete my mission.

299
00:25:24.290 --> 00:25:25.840
That's the idea!

300
00:25:27.010 --> 00:25:29.630
My mission is to waste your time!

301
00:25:52.030 --> 00:25:54.370
What to do...?

302
00:25:57.410 --> 00:25:59.000
Hold it!

303
00:26:12.260 --> 00:26:13.760
What's the matter, Chopper?

304
00:26:14.260 --> 00:26:15.640
Well...

305
00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:17.600
I'm not sure what it is, but...

306
00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:21.060
What is this haunting presence?

307
00:26:38.660 --> 00:26:40.620
What in the world...?

308
00:26:41.660 --> 00:26:44.960
Stand down, pacifista.

309
00:26:53.800 --> 00:26:54.970
What?!

310
00:26:54.970 --> 00:26:58.010
The pacifista have stopped escorting us!

311
00:26:58.010 --> 00:26:59.760
Come on, pacifista!

312
00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:01.720
You're supposed to keep us safe!

313
00:27:01.720 --> 00:27:04.140
I gave you an order!

314
00:27:04.890 --> 00:27:06.900
What's up with this?!

315
00:27:08.980 --> 00:27:12.320
The only ones above us
in the authority hierarchy...

316
00:27:12.740 --> 00:27:13.950
are...

317
00:27:14.860 --> 00:27:16.740
the Five Elders!

318
00:27:20.120 --> 00:27:21.290
Are we under attack?!

319
00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:34.380
A summoning circle?!

320
00:27:45.270 --> 00:27:46.440
What the hell?!

321
00:27:46.440 --> 00:27:48.940
Something's off! We need
to get to higher ground!

322
00:27:48.940 --> 00:27:49.650
Right!

323
00:27:53.530 --> 00:27:55.240
Attention, all Marines on land!

324
00:27:55.610 --> 00:28:00.700
St. Saturn of the Five Elders
will make landfall on Egghead shortly!

325
00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:05.410
No one below the rank of commodore
is permitted to behold him!

326
00:28:06.660 --> 00:28:07.870
An Elder?!

327
00:28:07.870 --> 00:28:09.330
I repeat!

328
00:28:09.330 --> 00:28:13.920
St. Saturn of the Five Elders
will make landfall on Egghead shortly!

329
00:28:21.720 --> 00:28:24.140
What the hell is up with that explosion?!

330
00:28:24.720 --> 00:28:28.480
The Five Elders?! One of them
came all the way to the island?!

331
00:28:28.480 --> 00:28:29.850
"Five Elders"?!

332
00:28:29.850 --> 00:28:31.520
Who the hell are they?!

333
00:28:31.520 --> 00:28:33.570
Only the highest authority in the world!

334
00:28:33.570 --> 00:28:34.980
What?!

335
00:28:57.840 --> 00:28:59.220
Something's coming out...!

336
00:29:25.620 --> 00:29:26.870
What is that?!

337
00:29:26.870 --> 00:29:28.370
It's a monster...!

338
00:29:28.370 --> 00:29:29.290
Don't say that!

339
00:29:29.620 --> 00:29:31.210
It has to be...

340
00:29:40.010 --> 00:29:41.760
The surface...

341
00:29:43.340 --> 00:29:45.180
It has been a while...

342
00:29:46.180 --> 00:29:50.140
<b>St. Jaygarcia Saturn
Godhead of Science and Defense
Five Elders, Highest Authority of the World Government</b>

343
00:29:50.140 --> 00:29:52.350
Is that some kind of monster?!

344
00:29:54.520 --> 00:29:55.520
Look up!

345
00:29:55.520 --> 00:29:56.480
Swerve!

346
00:30:00.150 --> 00:30:02.360
Oops...

347
00:30:02.360 --> 00:30:04.570
That was close...

348
00:30:04.570 --> 00:30:06.780
Oh no! The island clouds...!

349
00:30:09.500 --> 00:30:10.910
Kizaru!

350
00:30:14.170 --> 00:30:17.880
Hold it right there, Kizaru!

351
00:30:18.420 --> 00:30:22.800
You have to be reaching
your limit with that form by now...

352
00:30:22.800 --> 00:30:24.800
Please, Luffy!

353
00:30:24.800 --> 00:30:28.810
Do something!

354
00:30:35.520 --> 00:30:36.360
I'm on it–

355
00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:46.660
Gum-Gum...

356
00:30:49.580 --> 00:30:51.620
Star...

357
00:30:52.330 --> 00:30:53.040
Gun!

358
00:31:06.970 --> 00:31:10.060
Well now... this isn't good.

359
00:31:15.770 --> 00:31:17.230
Nika...

360
00:31:26.570 --> 00:31:28.370
Time's up...

361
00:31:41.250 --> 00:31:43.590
Are you okay, Vegapunk?!

362
00:31:43.590 --> 00:31:45.590
Not to worry, I'm alright.

363
00:31:45.590 --> 00:31:47.590
Atlas, are you hurt?!

364
00:31:47.590 --> 00:31:48.550
I'm fine!

365
00:31:55.600 --> 00:31:57.310
Are you St. Saturn?

366
00:31:57.310 --> 00:31:58.860
Indeed I am.

367
00:32:01.320 --> 00:32:05.780
I was certain we had
killed you already, Vegapunk.

368
00:32:13.120 --> 00:32:16.580
I gave you an order, Vegapunk.

369
00:32:26.090 --> 00:32:27.130
Bonney!

370
00:32:30.090 --> 00:32:34.060
You are not to leave him an ounce of free will!

371
00:32:36.730 --> 00:32:39.900
But if I do that, then Kuma...

372
00:32:55.870 --> 00:32:59.830
St. Saturn!
